{"tool":"markdownlint","language":"markdown","toolchainVersion":null,"docsVersion":"agent-read","source":"agent:https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md","docsBase":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md","fetchedAt":"2026-06-21T01:36:09.382Z","checksum":"sha256:85d6a88373029e51c8fc647b01fdfaa7d8749605bb88e15a92d127f5dc5cbfe4","ruleCount":53,"rules":[{"id":"MD001","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Heading levels should only increment by one level at a time","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md001","exampleBad":"# Heading 1\n\n### Heading 3\n\nWe skipped out a 2nd level heading in this document"},{"id":"MD003","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Heading style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md003"},{"id":"MD004","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Unordered list style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md004","exampleBad":"* Item 1\n+ Item 2\n- Item 3"},{"id":"MD005","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Inconsistent indentation for list items at the same level","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md005","exampleBad":"* Item 1\n  * Nested Item 1\n  * Nested Item 2\n   * A misaligned item"},{"id":"MD007","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Unordered list indentation","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md007","exampleBad":"* List item\n   * Nested list item indented by 3 spaces"},{"id":"MD009","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Trailing spaces","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md009","exampleBad":"Text text text\ntext[2 spaces]"},{"id":"MD010","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Hard tabs","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md010","exampleBad":"Some text\n\n\t* hard tab character used to indent the list item"},{"id":"MD011","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Reversed link syntax","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md011","exampleBad":"(Incorrect link syntax)[https://www.example.com/]"},{"id":"MD012","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Multiple consecutive blank lines","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md012","exampleBad":"Some text here\n\n\nSome more text here"},{"id":"MD013","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Line length","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md013","exampleBad":"IF THIS LINE IS THE MAXIMUM LENGTH\nThis line is okay because there are-no-spaces-beyond-that-length\nThis line is a violation because there are spaces beyond that length\nThis-line-is-okay-because-there-are-no-spaces-anywhere-within"},{"id":"MD014","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Dollar signs used before commands without showing output","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md014","exampleBad":"$ ls\n$ cat foo\n$ less bar"},{"id":"MD018","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"No space after hash on atx style heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md018","exampleBad":"#Heading 1\n\n##Heading 2"},{"id":"MD019","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Multiple spaces after hash on atx style heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md019"},{"id":"MD020","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"No space inside hashes on closed atx style heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md020","exampleBad":"#Heading 1#\n\n##Heading 2##"},{"id":"MD021","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Multiple spaces inside hashes on closed atx style heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md021"},{"id":"MD022","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Headings should be surrounded by blank lines","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md022"},{"id":"MD023","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Headings must start at the beginning of the line","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md023","exampleBad":"Some text\n\n  # Indented heading"},{"id":"MD024","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Multiple headings with the same content","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md024"},{"id":"MD025","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Multiple top-level headings in the same document","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md025","exampleBad":"# Top level heading\n\n# Another top-level heading"},{"id":"MD026","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Trailing punctuation in heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md026","exampleBad":"# This is a heading."},{"id":"MD027","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Multiple spaces after blockquote symbol","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md027","exampleBad":">  This is a blockquote with bad indentation\n>  there should only be one."},{"id":"MD028","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Blank line inside blockquote","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md028","exampleBad":"> This is a blockquote\n> which is immediately followed by\n\n> this blockquote. In some cases,\n> these may be merged into one blockquote."},{"id":"MD029","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Ordered list item prefix","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md029","exampleBad":"1. Do this.\n1. Do that.\n1. Done."},{"id":"MD030","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Spaces after list markers","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md030","exampleBad":"* Foo\n* Bar\n* Baz\n\n1. Foo\n1. Bar\n1. Baz\n\n1. Foo\n   * Bar\n1. Baz"},{"id":"MD031","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Fenced code blocks should be surrounded by blank lines","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md031","exampleBad":"Some text"},{"id":"MD032","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Lists should be surrounded by blank lines","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md032","exampleBad":"Some text\n* List item\n* List item\n\n1. List item\n2. List item\n***"},{"id":"MD033","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Inline HTML","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md033","exampleBad":"<h1>Inline HTML heading</h1>"},{"id":"MD034","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Bare URL used","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md034","exampleBad":"For more info, visit https://www.example.com/ or email user@example.com."},{"id":"MD035","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Horizontal rule style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md035","exampleBad":"---\n\n- - -\n\n***\n\n* * *\n\n****"},{"id":"MD036","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Emphasis used instead of a heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md036","exampleBad":"**My document**\n\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet...\n\n_Another section_\n\nConsectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod."},{"id":"MD037","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Spaces inside emphasis markers","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md037","exampleBad":"Here is some ** bold ** text.\n\nHere is some * italic * text.\n\nHere is some more __ bold __ text.\n\nHere is some more _ italic _ text."},{"id":"MD038","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Spaces inside code span elements","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md038","exampleBad":"`some text `\n\n` some text`\n\n`   some text   `"},{"id":"MD039","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Spaces inside link text","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md039","exampleBad":"[ a link ](https://www.example.com/)"},{"id":"MD040","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Fenced code blocks should have a language specified","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md040"},{"id":"MD041","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"First line in a file should be a top-level heading","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md041","exampleBad":"This is a document without a heading"},{"id":"MD042","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"No empty links","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md042","exampleBad":"[an empty link]()"},{"id":"MD043","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Required heading structure","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md043"},{"id":"MD044","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Proper names should have the correct capitalization","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md044","exampleBad":"[\n    \"JavaScript\"\n]"},{"id":"MD045","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Images should have alternate text (alt text)","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md045","exampleBad":"![Alternate text](image.jpg)"},{"id":"MD046","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Code block style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md046","exampleBad":"# Fenced code"},{"id":"MD047","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Files should end with a single newline character","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md047","exampleBad":"# Heading\n\nThis file ends without a newline.[EOF]"},{"id":"MD048","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Code fence style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md048"},{"id":"MD049","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Emphasis style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md049","exampleBad":"*Text*\n_Text_"},{"id":"MD050","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Strong style","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md050","exampleBad":"**Text**\n__Text__"},{"id":"MD051","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Link fragments should be valid","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md051","exampleBad":"# Heading Name\n\n[Link](#fragment)"},{"id":"MD052","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Reference links and images should use a label that is defined","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md052","exampleBad":"Full: [text][label]\nCollapsed: [label][]\nShortcut: [label]\n\nFull: ![text][image]\nCollapsed: ![image][]\nShortcut: ![image]\n\n[label]: https://example.com/label\n[image]: https://example.com/image"},{"id":"MD053","category":"style","severity":"medium","description":"Link and image reference definitions should be needed","source":"https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md#md053","exampleBad":"[//]: 